entry.title: Thelymitra malvina
entry.content: New species record for Wilsons Prom. Nearest records are west of Korumburra and Providence Ponds Reserve (east of Sale). Distinctive mauve tufts on column arms. Apparently opens only in mornings. These were open in pouring rain (no sun).
